    <div class="readpage_body_nr_01_a">
     抗战之超级兵锋&middot;最新章节 第一章：民国，我来了！
    </div> 
    <div class="readpage_body_nr_01_b">
     <div class="fl">
      <a href="http://www.sikushu.net/">首页</a> &raquo; 
      <a href="/modules/article/index.php?class=4">历史军事</a> &raquo; 
      <a href="index.html" target="_blank">抗战之超级兵锋最新章节</a>
     </div>
     <div class="fr">
      <a href="http://www.sikushu.net/dushu/97237.html"><font color="red">抗战之超级兵锋TXT全文下载</font></a> | 
      <a href="http://www.sikushu.net/modules/article/reviews.php?aid=97237&amp;type=all"><font color="#754AA2">评论</font></a> | 
